<DOCNO> LA021894-0048 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 014576 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 18, 1994, Friday, Home Edition 
</P>
