<P>
 Moorpark City Councilman Scott Montgomery was selected Thursday to serve for 
one year as chairman of the Ventura County Waste Commission. 
</P>
<P>
 Montgomery, vice-chair for four years, replaces Ventura County Supervisor 
Maggie Kildee at a time when the commission is preparing to establish a 
countywide regional waste authority. 
</P>
