 "Our primary objective over the coming year will be to create a single waste 
authority," Montgomery said. "We have been planning for this for four years; 
now it's just a matter of getting it done." 
</P>
<P>
 The commission is a countywide board with representatives from 10 cities; it 
was formed to coordinate management of waste issues in the county. MATTHEW MOSK 
