<P>
Profile; Infobox 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA021894-0145 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 014673 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 18, 1994, Friday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Valley Life; Page 10 
