<P>
 Residents of Rancho Santa Margarita have scheduled a flashlight walk for 5 
p.m. Sunday to call attention to the abduction of a 4-year-old boy who was 
taken last weekend from his foster home. 
</P>
<P>
 The community-walk sponsors are asking people to gather at the Rancho Santa 
