<TEXT>
<P>
 Flowers led the way to romance at the Valentine's Dinner Dance sponsored by 
the Black Singles of Orange County. Crimson carnations were handed out to 
everyone attending Sunday's heart-beating event at Randell's Jazz Club in Santa 
Ana. 
</P>
